<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="81">The specific epithet is a noun in the genitive case honouring Lucas Silveira Lecci, for his friendship and prolific fieldwork.</paragraph>
